{"tid":6161,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"QS大學畢業生就業能力排名榜　港大第18位","createTime":"2016-11-27T08:14:08.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-28T17:03:11.000Z","uid":5063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9ded16668e1f7aa5868a8d5257224b0d8003e8d7","tid":6161,"uid":5063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T08:14:08.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=N3QkE9bSYQyAbLB4T37GqsW%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=0b49013b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】國際高等教育及人力資源研究機構Quacquarelli Symonds(QS)公布「2017年全球大學畢業生就業能力排名」，香港共有3間大學成功打入榜上首300大，包括香港大學、香港中文大學及香港城市大學，當中以香港大學排名最高，在全球排名第18位，中大排名101至150名，而城大則排名201+，即200名至300名之間。 <br />\n<br />\nQS全球大學畢業生就業能力排名，以5項指標評估全球300間大學，包括全球37,000名僱主評價、校友成就、與僱主合作夥伴關係、僱主與學生之間聯繫，以及畢業生就業率等。 <br />\n<br />\n新公布大學畢業生就業能力排名榜中，以100分為滿分，美國史丹福大學以總分95.9分排名榜首，美國麻省理工學院及內地清華大學，則分別排名第二及第三。 <br />\n<br />\n香港方面，香港大學以總分77.1分排第18位，當中與僱主合作夥伴關係分項得分最高，達93.9分，但僱主與學生之間聯繫的分項得分最低，僅得68.4分；至於僱主評價則有89.1分，而畢業生就業率為88.1%。"},{"pid":"b0df7ab5f2472c7e24bfc438273aec9d3c6932ac","tid":6161,"uid":14119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T09:09:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71c08cc87102df2d2639d707a97ca01f6b07cc15","tid":6161,"uid":29238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T09:33:54.000Z","msg":"打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"686f56cc26289a27c19fb8f9bfd8b2a71b206680","tid":6161,"uid":5063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T10:40:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">而城大則排名201+，即200名至300名之間。</span>"},{"pid":"3e2ba2aaf5edb523f57504e34c80bfc65813ffc3","tid":6161,"uid":10620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T20:34:51.000Z","msg":"城大正式穩坐新三大寶座<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1797d0947e36c5219a77406142573584e6934389","tid":6161,"uid":5063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T05:40:44.000Z","msg":"讀UST都搵唔到工真係唔好讀好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0ba872c39129bc79b1be4b223b94d78547af12e","tid":6161,"uid":6122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T08:08:18.000Z","msg":"IN HKU WE TRUST<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bb780e990e9fab832c96e5fe93eaa978bfc5eb6","tid":6161,"uid":5063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T13:06:04.000Z","msg":"No one gives a shit?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f63d180eaa8c0d4497564d904ee15b3d8326c727","tid":6161,"uid":36690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T17:03:11.000Z","msg":"Shitty is da breast! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}